			<DIV>Yes I am suggesting permanent "worlds" of like 3 or 4 zones that are removed from the rest, but that you can zone into any time you want, like arena's except cross server, and limited to people within your "power range" taken into account level, AA and gear. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>That way you can PvE as you wish on your home server and then just zone into some fair pvp any time you wish, no immotal healing, and play for points on the leaderboard, if you die you return to your bind, full gear, full mana, all buffs you had when you died and like 3 minute stun. Make it accessable from the bazzar so you zone into the pvp world bazzar from yours, not some out of the way place like the arena, and make it cross server so that there will more then likely always be someone in your power range to fight. And instead of the cramped arena it would be like Bazz, Nexus, PoK, PoT and a few other zones or those 4 are more then enough. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
