<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Safe Zones...Get rid of them.&nbsp; All of them.&nbsp; Bazaar included.&nbsp; How you say?&nbsp; Easy.&nbsp; Make it so that you can flag one character on your account (under level 6)&nbsp;to -PVP.&nbsp; This toon would become a bazaar mule.&nbsp; The change would not be reversable.&nbsp; The names would be in blue just like an NPC.&nbsp; This toon should not be able to leave the bazaar and not be buffable or affected by spells.&nbsp; How you say?&nbsp; Well the flag system is already in place in game, make it so that the character is not able to zone out...OR...cause the character to have it's weight adjusted so high it is unable to move at all once it leaves the bazaar....just some suggestions, I am sure the devs can think of something better.&nbsp; How do I sell my stuff or buy stuff in the bazaar then?&nbsp; Easy...shared bank.&nbsp; Done deal.&nbsp; Safe zones gone....happy happy joy joy.</DIV>
