			>
			<DIV>Are pure melees getting slaughtered by pure casters ?&nbsp; I have found casters have an extremely difficult time getting a cast off, much less 13 or so casts it takes to kill a melee.&nbsp;&nbsp; Remember, there is also a huge discrepency on upper end HP at the moment.&nbsp; Melees often sit at 10K + hp, casters are lucky to see 4.5 K + (pure casters).&nbsp;&nbsp; Stuns have been increased, as have the melee radius..this seems to increase the problem, not reduce it.</DIV>	
